HEADWORD: Odinism
<hw>O"din*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Worship of Odin;
broadly, the Teutonic heathenism.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>O"din*ist</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms></p>

<p><q><qex>Odinism</qex> was valor; Christianism was humility, a nobler
kind of valor.</q> <rj><qau>Carlyle.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Odious</ent>⟦br⟧
